<p>Run Behat so it'll generate the missing definition. Selenium pops open the browser,
then fails. Copy the new definition into <code>FeatureContext</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="36336d7361">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
